=head1 Description

The B<Gnome::Gtk4::Orientable> interface is implemented by all widgets that can be
oriented horizontally or vertically.

B<Gnome::Gtk4::Orientable> is more flexible in that it allows the orientation to be
changed at runtime, allowing the widgets to “flip”.
